## 🔒 Security

### 🟡 Medium — JWT Secret Fallback
If `JWT_SECRET` env var is not set, `local_auth.go` falls back to a hardcoded or weak
default. Make startup fail loudly if no secret is configured in production:
```go
secret := os.Getenv("JWT_SECRET")
if secret == "" {
    log.Fatal("JWT_SECRET must be set")
}
```

### 🟡 Medium — CORS Allows All Origins
The CORS middleware in `api.go` allows `*` by default. In production this should be
restricted to the dashboard's own origin.

### 🟢 Low — `.env` in `.gitignore` ✅
Already done — good.

